{"tid":1740940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"糧盡煤氣斷 少女「煮婦」頂硬上","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T04:20:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f641318f8cd9f10a544512be351fd51330109c07","tid":1740940,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191120/K5B6S2HZEPDP4EX3JB5YNS26QQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191120%2FK5B6S2HZEPDP4EX3JB5YNS26QQ%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=606cf364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191120%2FK5B6S2HZEPDP4EX3JB5YNS26QQ%2F&h=f78d7e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191120/K5B6S2HZEPDP4EX3JB5YNS26QQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n糧盡煤氣斷 少女「煮婦」頂硬上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】留守理大校園的人，除了出外抗戰的「衝衝子」，亦有守護孩子成員、義務急救員等後勤支援人員，其中有未成年女生甘願擔任校園「背後的女人」，擔起主廚責任，雖然巧婦難為無米之炊，她面對糧食盡煤氣絕的惡劣環境，仍不斷想盡辦法調配及補給，留至最後一刻。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：手足：想食pizza可能係最後一餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191120/large/1574181252_a91f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191120%2Flarge%2F1574181252_a91f.gif&h=f4c16ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少女Kathy在理大飯堂負責水吧，為手足沖調飲品。邵靖妍攝<br />\n為前線叉足電<br />\n<br />\n自警方包圍理大，位於邵逸夫樓地下的大學飯堂，由抗爭者全面接管，更名為「抗爭飯堂」，自行派人洗切、調味、烹煮一腳踢，其中不足18歲的Kathy是飯堂義工一員。她稱自己只負責摺衫、派發物資、水吧等後勤角色，希望能發揮少少影響力，為前線拼搏的手足「叉足電」：「只要呢度有一個人需要我沖杯嘢飲畀佢，我都願意沖。」<br />\n<br />\n校園留守者曾多達800人以上，飯堂內劃出「日常用品」、「食物（乾）」、「食物（即食）」等區域，雖無人看守，抗爭者仍會排隊領取食物，秩序井然。其後煤氣中斷，加上食物資源越來越短缺，Kathy均要「諗過度過」，盡量讓食物平分至各人手上。<br />\n<br />\nKathy至今未敢向家人坦白將要面對被捕風險，僅告訴他們「自己嘅角色」好安全，為的就是讓他們安心，並默默承受壓力，「一定會擔心嘅，咁多人走咗，我留喺度，會唔會有更多嘅危險？到𠵱家嘅感覺，佢哋（警察）完全係想殺咗我哋。」她堅持留守到最後一刻，「我會留喺度陪前線行埋最後一步。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者邵靖妍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191120/large/1574181251_a5d8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191120%2Flarge%2F1574181251_a5d8.gif&h=2b5e0673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飯堂無人看守，但抗爭者領取食物時仍會守秩序排隊。"},{"pid":"81c225a61f19267fa5d33c9fe391ad09837e16a4","tid":1740940,"uid":333470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"697104876625f0a583067ff123af3858fd43e96f","tid":1740940,"uid":250979,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"辛苦手足kathy.."},{"pid":"42835b6dbcc3a0bfa75fe6329c3e9f27eb332657","tid":1740940,"uid":59868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"每個人只要心不死<br />\n就總有一個位可以參與抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b111d9fe35786bea1e2e0fb730508eea589b000f","tid":1740940,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />守望相助"},{"pid":"eff05f75a2306c83cc4c9cc3baf9e5076da02b4c","tid":1740940,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"手足..."},{"pid":"f0df05c06ddb29470fbf87c5617c116a149d4a61","tid":1740940,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c503c6dcf51681bb003dc6159e5a9cc5f5de6135","tid":1740940,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42835b6dbcc3a0bfa75fe6329c3e9f27eb332657","tid":1740940,"uid":59868,"like":5,