：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=21e0ff04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=2225da0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"52ecf970d544339d5e432cacdf68916b3713009d","tid":1740940,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"支持手足"},{"pid":"8e3588c24fedb613e51e63915377df17d6ab5336","tid":1740940,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b24fe62d527d6685dba1bdcada302f720db3f445","tid":1740940,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"依家理大重有手足係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔救全部捉到會告暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係紅隧春袋搞到大塞車佢地唔做文宣<br />\n佢地卻聯合藍絲跳出來賴手足搞到塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}